#: eeschema/dialogs/dialog_bom_help_md.h:2
msgid ""
"# 1. Summary\n"
"\n"
"The Bill of Materials tool creates a BOM which lists all of the components "
"in the design.\n"
"\n"
"The tool uses an external script to generate a BOM in the desired output "
"format. Choosing a different script changes how the BOM is formatted.\n"
"\n"
"Generating a BOM is described in more detail in the Schematic Editor "
"manual.\n"
"\n"
"# 2. Usage\n"
"\n"
"Select a generator script in the **BOM generator scripts** list. Details for "
"the selected generator are shown on the right of the dialog.\n"
"\n"
"Clicking the **Generate** button creates a BOM file with the selected "
"generator.\n"
"\n"
"The default settings present several generator script options, although some "
"additional scripts are installed with KiCad and can be added to the list "
"with the **+** button.\n"
"\n"
"**Note:** On Windows, there is an additional option **Show console window**. "
"When this option is unchecked, BOM generators run in a hidden console window "
"and any output is redirected and printed in the dialog. When this option is "
"checked, BOM generators run in a visible console window.\n"
"\n"
"# 3. Custom generators and command lines\n"
"\n"
"Internally, KiCad creates an intermediate netlist file in XML format that "
"contains information about all of the components in the design. A BOM "
"generator script converts the intermediate netlist file to the desired "
"output format. KiCad runs the BOM generator scripts according to the command "
"line entered at the bottom of the BOM dialog.\n"
"\n"
"The command line format accepts parameters for filenames. Each formatting "
"parameter is replaced with a project-specific path or filename. The "
"supported formatting parameters are:\n"
"\n"
" * `%I`: absolute path and filename of the intermediate netlist file, which "
"is the input to the BOM generator\n"
" * `%O`: absolute path and filename of the output BOM file (without file "
"extension)\n"
" * `%B`: base filename of the output BOM file (without file extension)\n"
" * `%P`: absolute path of the project directory, without trailing slash\n"
"\n"
"**Note:** the `%O` output file parameter does not include a file extension. "
"KiCad will attempt to add an appropriate extension to the command line "
"automatically, but an extension may need to be added by hand.\n"
"\n"
"Python is the recommended tool for BOM generator scripts, but other tools "
"can also be used.\n"
"\n"
"## Example command lines for Python scripts\n"
"\n"
"The command line format for a Python script is of the form:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"python <script file name> <input filename> <output filename>\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"On Windows, if the desired generator script for a CSV BOM is `C:"
"\\Users\\username\\kicad\\my_python_script.py`, the command line would be:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"python.exe C:\\Users\\username\\kicad\\my_python_script.py \"%I\" \"%O."
"csv\"\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"On Linux, if the desired generator script for a CSV BOM is `/home/username/"
"kicad/my_python_script.py`, the command line would be:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"python /home/username/kicad/my_python_script.py \"%I\" \"%O.csv\"\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Double quotes (`\"`) around the arguments are recommended in case filenames "
"contain spaces or special characters.\n"
msgstr ""
"# 1. Ringkasan\n"
"\n"
"Alat Daftar Material membuat BOM yang mencantumkan semua komponen dalam "
"desain.\n"
"\n"
"Alat ini menggunakan skrip eksternal untuk menghasilkan BOM dalam format "
"keluaran yang diinginkan. Memilih skrip yang berbeda mengubah cara "
"pemformatan BOM.\n"
"\n"
"Pembuatan BOM dijelaskan lebih rinci dalam manual Penyunting Skematik.\n"
"\n"
"# 2. Penggunaan\n"
"\n"
"Pilih skrip generator di daftar **Skrip generator BOM**. Detail untuk "
"generator yang dipilih ditampilkan di sisi kanan dialog.\n"
"\n"
"Mengklik tombol **Hasilkan** membuat berkas BOM dengan generator yang "
"dipilih.\n"
"\n"
"Pengaturan bawaan menyediakan beberapa opsi skrip generator, meskipun "
"beberapa skrip tambahan diinstal bersama KiCad dan dapat ditambahkan ke "
"daftar dengan tombol **+**.\n"
"\n"
"**Catatan:** Di Windows, terdapat opsi tambahan **Tampilkan jendela "
"konsol**. Jika opsi ini tidak dicentang, generator BOM berjalan di jendela "
"konsol tersembunyi dan setiap keluaran dialihkan dan dicetak dalam dialog. "
"Jika opsi ini dicentang, generator BOM berjalan di jendela konsol yang "
"terlihat.\n"
"\n"
"# 3. Generator kustom dan baris perintah\n"
"\n"
"Secara internal, KiCad membuat berkas netlist perantara dalam format XML "
"yang berisi informasi tentang semua komponen dalam desain. Skrip generator "
"BOM mengonversi berkas netlist perantara ke format keluaran yang diinginkan. "
"KiCad menjalankan skrip generator BOM sesuai baris perintah yang dimasukkan "
"di bagian bawah dialog BOM.\n"
"\n"
"Format baris perintah menerima parameter untuk nama berkas. Setiap parameter "
"pemformatan diganti dengan jalur atau nama berkas yang spesifik untuk "
"proyek. Parameter pemformatan yang didukung adalah:\n"
"\n"
" * `%I`: jalur absolut dan nama berkas dari berkas netlist perantara, yang "
"merupakan masukan untuk generator BOM\n"
" * `%O`: jalur absolut dan nama berkas dari berkas BOM keluaran (tanpa "
"ekstensi berkas)\n"
" * `%B`: nama berkas dasar dari berkas BOM keluaran (tanpa ekstensi berkas)\n"
" * `%P`: jalur absolut dari direktori proyek, tanpa garis miring akhir\n"
"\n"
"**Catatan:** parameter berkas keluaran `%O` tidak menyertakan ekstensi "
"berkas. KiCad akan mencoba menambahkan ekstensi yang sesuai ke baris "
"perintah secara otomatis, tetapi ekstensi mungkin perlu ditambahkan secara "
"manual.\n"
"\n"
"Python adalah alat yang direkomendasikan untuk skrip generator BOM, tetapi "
"alat lain juga dapat digunakan.\n"
"\n"
"## Contoh baris perintah untuk skrip Python\n"
"\n"
"Format baris perintah untuk skrip Python berbentuk:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"python <nama berkas skrip> <nama berkas masukan> <nama berkas keluaran>\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Di Windows, jika skrip generator yang diinginkan untuk BOM CSV adalah `C:"
"\\Users\\username\\kicad\\my_python_script.py`, baris perintahnya adalah:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"python.exe C:\\Users\\username\\kicad\\my_python_script.py \"%I\" \"%O."
"csv\"\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Di Linux, jika skrip generator yang diinginkan untuk BOM CSV adalah `/home/"
"username/kicad/my_python_script.py`, baris perintahnya adalah:\n"
"\n"
"```\n"
"python /home/username/kicad/my_python_script.py \"%I\" \"%O.csv\"\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Tanda kutip ganda (`\"`) di sekeliling argumen direkomendasikan jika nama "
"berkas mengandung spasi atau karakter khusus.\n"

