#: pcbnew/dialogs/panel_setup_constraints_base.cpp:114
msgid ""
"The minimum annular ring width. If set, this can only be reduced by custom "
"rules."
msgstr ""
"Lebar cincin annular minimum. Jika disetel, hanya dapat dikurangi dengan "
"aturan kustom."

